A: You can use StringTokenizer to split the path into parts.
StringTokenizer st = new StringTokenizer(path, "/");
String[] parts = new String[st.countTokens()];
for (int i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {
    parts[i] = st.nextToken();
}
